headline: Arch Capital Group Ltd. to Report 2024 Fourth Quarter Results on February 10
summary: PEMBROKE, Bermuda, January 09, 2025--Arch Capital Group Ltd. (NASDAQ: ACGL, "the Company") today announced it expects to release its 2024 fourth quarter results after the close of regular stock market hours on Monday, February 10. The Company will hold a conference call for investors and analysts at 11 a.m. ET on Tuesday, February 11.
